data.description: Great 3bdr 2bth home with large family room/den.  This home has been lovingly cared for by its current owner for over 45 years.  As you enter the home you’re greeted by the family room adjacent to your formal dining room.  The family room is inundated with natural light from the large windows on the front and rear of the home.  The kitchen features oak cabinets, tile counter tops, and tile flooring.  The interior laundry room is off the kitchen and is spacious enough for a washer and dryer.  The hallway has beautiful oak flooring.  The primary bedroom has carpet flooring, a ceiling fan, and a generously sized closet.  The primary bathroom has a walk in shower with tile flooring.  The secondary bedrooms are spacious and have carpet flooring.  The hall bathroom has a tub, a vanity, and has tile flooring.  The family room/den off the bedrooms is a great space for you to relax in or to turn into a game room, entertainment room, or an additional family room.  Very versatile. The backyard is very private, it has a lawn area, a patio slab, and mature landscaping.  The front driveway features a covered carport, roomy enough for two large vehicles.  Stop by this charming home located in a beautiful neighborhood close to Sofi Stadium, schools and shopping.
